TITLE: Performing Hybrid Search with Swift SDK
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to implement hybrid search using the Orama Swift client. Includes document structure definition and search parameter configuration with optional limit, offset, and field selection.
SOURCE: https://github.com/oramasearch/orama/blob/main/packages/docs/src/content/docs/cloud/performing-search/hybrid-search.mdx#2025-04-11_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: swift
CODE:
```
import OramaCloudClient

struct MyDoc: Encodable & Decodable {
  let title: String
  let description: String
}

